EXTRACTED VALUE: While the first Mech title for the 360 isn’t exactly incredible, it does set a standard for online play that will only better with age.
Although we've been here many times before, Timeshift is still a slick shooter with some neat ideas. [Christmas 2007, p.83]
Personally, it works for me as there’s just something about see enemy legions running down a hill side in formation and then charging into battle.
